						<handDesc hands="1">
							<summary>Ashkenazi semi-cursive script, not punctuated. <name type="person" role="scribe">Yitsḥaḳ Merly</name>: inscribed with his name as an author of corrections in the text, folio 1r, in a following subscription: מתוקן על ידי יצחק מארלי. See similar subscription in Harley 5655, <ref target="Margoliouth_1965" type="number">180</ref>.</summary>
